不要無中生有。<br />\n<br />\n大波驊有關人士的陳詞濫調充滿了政治偏見與謊言。我要強調，中國內政不容任何外部反華勢力指手畫腳。中國一向秉持和平共處五項原則處理國與國關係，歷來堅定奉行不干涉內政原則，主張各國根據自身國情選擇發展道路。大波驊的拙劣表演充分暴露出其不可告人的險惡用心和政治企圖。<br />\n<br />\n中國堅持走和平發展道路，積極為維護世界和平穩定貢獻智慧力量。中國堅持對外開放，互利共贏，同世界分享中國發展的機遇。大波驊自己不願意投入，卻千方百計干擾破壞中國和其他國家開展合作。大波驊試圖挑撥中國共產黨和中國人民的關係，極其陰險。"},{"pid":"b589f1638400c1f7fb8566741ab39c5570d384ca","tid":1767401,"uid":20006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"係咪又仆街?"},{"pid":"b371cce5f04b09f918a18c25b7cf736a91f95e78","tid":1767401,"uid":90773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"係咪比共產黨截住咗"},{"pid":"e63fbfe943c36a281d6e6e43c6841d33f8c6b415","tid":1767401,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:18:51.000Z","msg":"青馬塞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4218470fd8d00d145969c872c8a3b0b1a144bfde","tid":1767401,"uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ece68dece1516ffbcff3e28f32a43d4279ea4ae5","tid":1767401,"uid":326725,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"高官返工守則：例遲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"其實好多香港人都遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31403db02e0ebc0535b80d85d1a4552d2081f09","tid":1767401,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b371cce5f04b09f918a18c25b7cf736a91f95e78","tid":1767401,"uid":90773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"係咪比共產黨截住咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:20:28.000Z","msg":"仲有咩人可以阻到司長級咁耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ca005e184c6800bb56735e6912e00cde3d7860","tid":1767401,"uid":10121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"遲撚左成個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g